com.paydiant.android.core.service

Class UserRegistrationManagerService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paydiant.android.core.service.UserRegistrationManagerService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IUserRegistrationManagerService

    public class UserRegistrationManagerService
extends Object
implements IUserRegistrationManagerService
    The Class UserRegistrationManagerService. The class contains the methods which are used to validate Email, Validate username, Retrieve MFA questions and Register user etc.

    Warning: DO NOT reference the core.service package classes directly as these are missing the required business functionalities. Use core.facade or ui.service classes instead.

    Author:
    Paydiant Inc.
